$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_min_level

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_min_level -  This method returns the minimum level of the potion name.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int query_min_level(string s)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^s%^RESET%^ - the name to lookup
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the minimum level
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/potion.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the minimum level of the potion name.  The
expand_nickname function will be done on the input name before
looking it up.
.EP

